                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation and application of vermiculite/tannic acid composite aerogel with adjustable surface energy",
                    "一种表面能可调的蛭石/单宁酸复合气凝胶的制备和应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of aerogel and hydrate technology application, and relates to preparation and application of vermiculite/tannic acid composite aerogel with adjustable surface energy. The vermiculite/tannic acid composite aerogel is used as a carrier to support a methionine solution, and the methionine solution is promoted to efficiently form a carbon dioxide hydrate with carbon dioxide under the conditions of low temperature and high pressure. As a hydrate reaction carrier, the prepared aerogel has the characteristics of high porosity and large specific surface area, the gas-liquid contact area in the reaction process of water and carbon dioxide is remarkably increased, rich nucleation sites are provided for hydration reaction, and carbon dioxide hydrate generation kinetics is remarkably enhanced. In addition, by controlling the use amount of tannic acid, the surface energy of the vermiculite/tannic acid composite aerogel can be regulated and controlled, the polar component of the material surface can be reduced, water molecules can be induced to form a proper hydrogen bond network on the aerogel surface, and the hydrate generation rate and the gas storage capacity can be improved. The method has the advantages of environmental friendliness, simple process, large gas storage capacity and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于气凝胶和水合物技术应用领域，一种表面能可调的蛭石/单宁酸复合气凝胶的制备和应用。利用蛭石/单宁酸复合气凝胶为载体担载甲硫氨酸溶液，促进甲硫氨酸溶液在低温高压的条件下与二氧化碳高效形成二氧化碳水合物。本发明制备的气凝胶作为水合物反应载体具有孔隙率高、比表面积大的特点，显著提升了水和二氧化碳反应过程中气液接触面积，并为水合反应提供了丰富的成核位点，显著强化了二氧化碳水合物生成动力学。此外，通过控制单宁酸的用量，可调控蛭石/单宁酸复合气凝胶的表面能，降低材料表面的极性分量，诱导水分子在气凝胶表面形成适宜的氢键网络，提升水合物生成的速率和储气量。本发明具有环境友好、工艺简单、储气量大等优点。"
                }
            ]
